2026-04-28T09:19:14.571+00:00 **⚠️ CRITICAL ISSUE:** The deletion command cascaded and deleted shared resources (`pvc/data-sync-storage` and `secret/db-credentials`). This is exactly what the runbook warned against - shared PVCs and Secrets were deleted which other services may depend on.

